<br />
<br />
NOTE:&nbsp;At least half of the credit hours required for a minor must be completed at UIC, and a minimum GPA of 2.0/4.0 is required in the minor field.<br />
<br />
<p>Minors offered by other UIC colleges and made available to LAS students are acceptable towards LAS undergraduate degrees. For a list of all minor options at UIC, access the <a href="http://catalog.uic.edu/ucat/degree-programs/degree-minors/">Degree Program and Minor List</a>&nbsp;in the UIC Undergraduate Catalog. Students should consult with the college offering the minor for more information about that particular minor. Not all minors are open to students from other colleges. &nbsp;<br />
<br />
<sup>*</sup>This minor requires a declared secondary education major.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
</p>


